In a certain coding language "light is best" is written as "pi pn so", "all is good" is written as "cu pn po" and "all the best" is written as "lu cu pi". What is the code used for "the" ? </br> एक निश्चित कोड भाषा में "light is best" को "pi pn so" लिखा जाता है, "all is good" को "cu pn po" लिखा जाता है तथा "all the best" को "lu cu pi" लिखा जाता है, तो "the" शब्द का कोड उस भाषा में क्या होगा ?@po@cu@lu@pi@3@